node.text: Meet my gal pal and Tennessee Walker, Spirit 🤠👁✨ YEEHAW FOR MY NEW HOBBY!!! Man oh man it’s so humbling being in the presence of these stunning creatures. I’m looking forward to learning more about horses, their care, and riding!!! Thank you for telling us about this special place @wildwestjc! We had a magical experience @704horsemen 🐎 you gentlemen were so welcoming, professional, and tons of fun. See you guys again soon…like…in a few days with apples too 🍏🥰🍎

node.text: From their breathtaking beauty, superior emotional intelligence, to being apex predators, it’s easy to understand why orcas are my favorite animal. When Keiko died of pneumonia after being released I cried. IYKYK! My love for killer whales is how I came across the truth about Sea World (and all animal attractions in general) after watching Blackfish. With that being said, I’d rather shit in my hands and clap than go to Sea World 😃 #BoycottSeaWorldDay @peta
